task.summary: Added comments to the TestResults, seeResults method to understand why the code is there and the issues associated with it.
Added a variation on the TreeGrid that has nested elements within it.
Added the new component to the main page app. Corrected the helper method to call the correct method from the Apex class.

Added LWC code and commenting, unfortunately, I am not sure why the data will not display on the page. It does show up appropriately in Anonymous Apex and the Web Page's console debug log.

added pagination, needs commenting and correction for bug introduced with disabling the button.
Added more commenting to explain what is going on and fixed the next and previous button bug.
Added sorting, changed from a combo box to a button with the icon being the sorting one. Implemented the sorting method to sort by the Id in reverse and forward order.
Removed the options that were associated with the combobox as they are no longer needed.
